GDE2-Applets
=============

https://github.com/gde2-desktop/gde2-applets

This package contains applets for use with the GDE2 panel.  Therefore, it
requires gde2-core to be installed.  To build all applets additional
libraries may be needed.

This list is by no means definitive.

GDE2-Applets is a fork of GNOME-Applets.


Requirements
------------

You need at least:

    gde2-panel
    gtk+-2.24.0
    glib-2.36.0
    libgtop-2.12.0
    libwnck

Some extras that improve functionality:

    libnotify
    dbus-0.34


Mailing List
------------

The mailing list for GDE2-Applets is gde2-dev@ml.gde2-desktop.org


Contributing to GDE2-Applets
-----------------------------

Read the HACKING file


Reporting Bugs
--------------

Bugs should be reported via GitHub
<https://github.com/gde2-desktop/gde2-applets/issues/>.

